ion is a newer .NET feature that might not apply to .NET 8, so I should focus on the project file changes instead. My approach is to remove the VSTest-specific dependencies, ensure the project is set up as an executable with `IsTestingPlatformApplication` enabled, and then test the changes to verify everything works.","outputTokens":1760,"requestId":"0C00:3B8D06:6A93893:73A0CC7:69F01712"},"id":"fac58510-ddd5-4bac-b041-9def05fef1f9","timestamp":"2026-04-28T02:10:56.703Z","parentId":"73136fbf-9bfd-42a9-a502-b98313338a59"}
